"如果域名为`mycompany.com`，请确保创建一个子域 `odoo._domainkey.mycompany.com` ，其规范名称为 "
"`odoo._domainkey.odoo.com.`。"

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_domain.rst:92
