msgstr ""
"可使用Excel (.xlsx) 或CSV (.csv) 格式导入Odoo业务对象的任何数据：联系人、产品、银行对账单、日记账条目、甚至订单！"

#: ../../content/applications/general/export_import_data.rst:72
msgid ""
"Open the view of the object you want to populate and click on "
